                <note type="authorial">over</note>
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.38.15-19_0005b"/>
                
                <note type="authorial">Since closing this I've read that article on Grierson, and I note that he was an old-timer. I never knew him or any of his stuff, and I doubt that the idea in question <hi rend="underline">did</hi> come from him. The article mentioned here is about G.'s "The Valley of the Shadows" J. N.</note>
                

                
